    <h1 class="display-4">Python Course</h1>
    <img src="/static/images/python-logo.png" alt="Python Logo" class="course-logo">
</div>

<div class="course-content">
    <h2>About the Course</h2>
    <p>Python is a powerful programming language with simple and clear syntax, perfect for beginners.</p>
    
    <h3>What You'll Learn:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Python syntax fundamentals</li>
        <li>Working with variables and data types</li>
